  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Notes</h2><strong>Trapper's Delight was originally envisioned as a party game. So we recommend that you gather your friends for a couch-play experience or play with them online. Please keep in mind that as an indie game with a small player base, it is not always possible to find players online.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=612 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><strong>Trapper's Delight</strong> is a game where players create a gauntlet of lethal contraptions and secret traps. Once all of the traps are in place, players have to try and navigate the traps in real-time along with the other competitors. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=612 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To score points in <strong>Trapper's Delight</strong>, players will need to reach the goal safely. To prevent others from scoring, create the most devious traps possible... but make sure you can navigate past them too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Feature Overview </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Local Multiplayer for 2-4 players (Requires at least one controller)<br></li><li> Online Multiplayer for 2-4 players<br></li><li> Single-player Challenge Mode with 48 Puzzle Levels<br></li><li> 28 Traps and Tiles to place<br></li><li> In-game Replays<br></li><li> Player customisation including lots of hats!<br></li><li> Create new multiplayer and challenge levels with the level editor and share levels on the Steam Workshop</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Notes</h2><strong>Trapper's Delight was originally envisioned as a party game. So we recommend that you gather your friends for a couch-play experience or play with them online. Please keep in mind that as an indie game with a small player base, it is not always possible to find players online.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=612 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/f627b102227fd371d3f52eb87f479140.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><strong>Trapper's Delight</strong> is a game where players create a gauntlet of lethal contraptions and secret traps. Once all of the traps are in place, players have to try and navigate the traps in real-time along with the other competitors. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=612 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/9feb54e589a06e791048b5be96917a8e.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To score points in <strong>Trapper's Delight</strong>, players will need to reach the goal safely. To prevent others from scoring, create the most devious traps possible... but make sure you can navigate past them too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.poster.avif?t=1563624499\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.webm?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467760/extras/7d61d9931588a047f7b30df61bc23fdd.mp4?t=1563624499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Feature Overview </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Local Multiplayer for 2-4 players (Requires at least one controller)<br></li><li> Online Multiplayer for 2-4 players<br></li><li> Single-player Challenge Mode with 48 Puzzle Levels<br></li><li> 28 Traps and Tiles to place<br></li><li> In-game Replays<br></li><li> Player customisation including lots of hats!<br></li><li> Create new multiplayer and challenge levels with the level editor and share levels on the Steam Workshop</li></ul>",
